## NEXT: Block 3 — ESP32-WROOM-32E-H4
- New file: mcu.trace_sch
- JLCPCB C3013935
- EN: 10k+1uF RC delay + reset button
- IO0: boot button
- RESERVED (do not use as peripherals): IO0, IO2, IO12, IO15
- IO12 must be LOW at boot (pull-down required)
- Power from V3V3 rail (global label from power_rails sheet)
- UART1 to SIM7080G modem (V3V8 domain - need level shift check)
- UART2 to ATGM336H GPS
- I2C: LSM6DS3TR-C + BQ34Z100-G1
- 1-Wire: DS18B20
- GPIO interrupt: A3144 hall sensor
